      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/admin/getting_started/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;setup-new-spaces&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Setup new spaces&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/admin/getting_started/#setup-new-spaces&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Setup new spaces&#34; href=&#34;#setup-new-spaces&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;At first, as superadmin you must create a space, create accounts for the future space administrators and give them &lt;em&gt;admin&lt;/em&gt; role to this space.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;First step is to connect with the configured admin account.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 id=&#34;create-a-space&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Create a space&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/admin/getting_started/#create-a-space&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Create a space&#34; href=&#34;#create-a-space&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the &lt;em&gt;admin&lt;/em&gt; menu, go to &lt;em&gt;Spaces&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../install_1.png&#34; alt=&#34;main page&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
